OL,7,FITV News has revealed that in July
OL,8,F2013, Second Sight told Chief
OL,9,FExecutive Paula Vennells in a secretly
OL,10,Frecorded meeting about serious issues
OL,11,Fwith Horizon, including allegations
OL,12,Fthat branch accounts could be remotely
OL,13,Faccessed by Fujitsu workers at its
OL,14,Fheadquarters in Bracknell.
OL,16,FThey also urged Ms Vennells and other
OL,17,FPost Office executives not to cover up
OL,18,Fthe problems.
