OL,7,FITV News possesses another secret
OL,8,Frecording of a meeting held on
OL,9,FDecember 5th 2013 with the then-Post
OL,10,FOffice General Counsel Chris Aujard,
OL,11,Fthe organisation's most senior lawyer,
OL,12,Fand Ian Henderson and Ron Warmington
OL,13,Ffrom Second Sight.
OL,15,FMr Aujard had been in the role for six
OL,16,Fweeks when the meeting took place.
OL,18,FMr Warmington outlines a catalogue of
OL,19,Ffailings by the Post Office in its
OL,20,Fpursuit and prosecution of sub-
OL,21,Fpostmasters.
