OL,7,FHe tells Mr Aujard: "In many cases,
OL,8,Fthere was the threat of a theft
OL,9,Fcharge, which was lifted as part of a
OL,10,Fdeal, sort of courtroom steps deal,
OL,11,Fwhere the condition was we won't
OL,12,Fpursue the theft charge - by the way
OL,13,Fwe wouldn't have had the information
OL,14,For the evidence to win anyway - as
OL,15,Flong as you plead guilty to the false
OL,16,Faccounting, and as long as you refrain
OL,17,Ffrom saying anything in your defence
OL,18,Fto do with the criticism of Horizon."
