OL,7,F"And all that's been happening is the
OL,8,Finvestigation team has been saying,
OL,9,F'So what did you do in that six
OL,10,Fmonths? Well, I carried it forward
OL,11,F'cause the help desk said the problem
OL,12,Fwould go away, it would sort itself
OL,13,Fout... I pretended I'd got the cash in
OL,14,Fthe till. Ah, so you've committed
OL,15,Ffalse accounting. Right? Thank you.
OL,17,F"Closed. Literally, you can hear the
OL,18,Fbook being slammed shut, and that's
OL,19,Fthe end of it.
