OL,7,F"What that meant is that Post Office
OL,8,FLimited proceeded to criminal
OL,9,Fprosecution without the underlying
OL,10,Ffactors having been investigated.
OL,12,F"Now, that is bloody serious because
OL,13,Fit would be a criminal offence to not
OL,14,Fyield up to the defence, evidence that
