OL,7,F"And yet it doesn't seem that either
OL,8,Fthe investigation team and the
OL,9,Fprosecution team knew that, or if they
OL,10,Fknew about it, they didn't cut her any
OL,11,Fslack because of it...and it's really
OL,12,Fserious 'cause it's potentially an
OL,13,Funsafe conviction."
OL,15,FIan Henderson adds: "We are
OL,16,Fconsistently seeing prosecutions that
OL,17,Fare focused on the false accounting
OL,18,Fissue with no regard for actually
OL,19,Fidentifying what has caused the
OL,20,Fdeficiency in the first place."
